Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.55,0:00:03.85,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,This was a terrible idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.85,0:00:07.77,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Does this skirt {\i1}have{\i0} to be so short?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.77,0:00:11.28,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,I'm 25 years old, dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.24,0:00:17.24,Signs,,0,0,0,,The 25 Year Old High School Girl
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.24,0:00:17.24,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\an1}Episode 1: An Unexpected Reunion
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.37,0:00:21.16,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,You want me to go to school {\i1}for{\i0} Kaho?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.16,0:00:23.62,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,That girl does nothing but go out with friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.62,0:00:26.49,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,She hasn't attended classes since she enrolled.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.49,0:00:28.40,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,At this rate, she'll have to repeat a year.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.40,0:00:30.67,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,No way! Not happening!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.67,0:00:32.39,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,You'll be fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.39,0:00:34.10,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,You and Kaho are practically twins!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.10,0:00:35.49,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,You can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.49,0:00:39.08,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Hana, I know you haven't found a new job yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.08,0:00:41.42,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)}I'll be sure to make it worth your time!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.79,0:00:44.46,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I ended up giving in...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.94,0:00:48.94,Signs,,0,0,0,,Mathematics: New Edition
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.46,0:00:47.22,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,...but I don't think I can keep this up.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.39,0:00:47.56,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Kaho. Kaho Miyoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.19,0:00:49.29,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.29,0:00:51.44,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,What's the matter? Are you not feeling well?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.01,0:00:55.45,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Yes. I umm... I have a headache.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.45,0:00:58.32,Signs,,0,0,0,,Nurse's Office
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.79,0:00:58.32,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm beat...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.32,0:01:01.70,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He told me to take a break and lie down.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.09,0:01:05.33,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Oh, hey Kaho. Skipping class again?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.07,0:01:09.84,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Why'd you leave karaoke early the other day?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.84,0:01:11.51,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,W-What do I say?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.51,0:01:14.80,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Is he a friend of Kaho's? He couldn't be her boyfriend...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.80,0:01:19.22,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,You know, I've always thought you were pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.22,0:01:20.81,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's really close!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.81,0:01:24.07,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Next time, come as my trophy girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.07,0:01:26.06,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,You've done that for other guys, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.45,0:01:30.89,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,What's going on in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.89,0:01:32.16,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Shit, it's Kanie.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.65,0:01:36.60,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,You've got a lot of energy for someone with such a terrible a fever, huh Aida?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.11,0:01:39.12,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,W-Well, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.05,0:01:39.12,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i0}He's {\i1}a teacher?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.57,0:01:42.44,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,If you're feeling better, go to class.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.44,0:01:44.25,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.25,0:01:45.89,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,"Yes {\i1}sir{\i0}."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.89,0:01:47.12,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.19,0:01:54.59,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,U-Umm, sir, I wasn't feeling well and so...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.53,0:01:58.07,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,It {\i1}is{\i0} you! You're Hana Natori.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.07,0:02:00.72,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Y-You're mistaken. I'm...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.46,0:02:00.72,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.72,0:02:03.19,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Have I been found out?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.19,0:02:05.77,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,So you really don't remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.71,0:02:09.16,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Well, it has been quite a while since graduation.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.77,0:02:13.27,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,I'm Akito Kanie. We were in the same class.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.27,0:02:15.78,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,You're {\i1}that{\i0} Kanie?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.41,0:02:17.87,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,What's that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.87,0:02:19.39,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Please, Kanie.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.39,0:02:21.79,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,I need you to keep quiet about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.79,0:02:23.66,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,You see, there's a very good reason for this...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.57,0:02:31.63,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,I see. I understand the situation, but I can't support such foolish behavior.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.63,0:02:33.47,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,W-Wait, Kanie!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.47,0:02:36.23,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,I told you, at this rate Kaho is going to be held back.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.23,0:02:37.92,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,We reap what we sow.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.27,0:02:40.49,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Besides, how do {\i1}you{\i0} feel about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.49,0:02:44.59,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,I don't think it's right, but she worked so hard to get into this school.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.59,0:02:46.31,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,You're still as softhearted as ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.67,0:02:50.17,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Kanie?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.17,0:02:53.31,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Do you know what to do to keep a man quiet?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.31,0:02:58.19,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A kiss?! But why? N-No...!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.28,0:03:01.69,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kanie, no!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.69,0:03:04.02,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,You're trembling after a simple kiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.47,0:03:06.79,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,You can't possibly be a real high school girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.79,0:03:08.74,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,That's because you didn't give me any warning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.45,0:03:13.12,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,And here I was thinking I'd just tease you a little...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.12,0:03:14.50,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,but if you're going to make that face...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.75,0:03:16.88,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,{\i1}N-No way!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.38,0:03:21.13,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,N-No! Stop it, Kanie!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.53,0:03:26.79,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,You want me to keep quiet, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.79,0:03:31.90,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Y-You can't. We're still in the nurse's office.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.78,0:03:39.68,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Just for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.21,0:03:45.03,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,I'll give you a special lesson I can't give to children.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.97,0:03:55.04,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This can't be happening. What do I do?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.71,0:04:00.42,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,{\i1}M-My body's not listening to me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.71,0:04:07.52,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,{\an8}You're not struggling very much now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.13,0:04:11.90,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,N-Not there...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.73,0:04:15.90,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,{\an8}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.47,0:04:24.44,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}How did it turn out like this?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.65,0:04:28.26,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}What's going to happen to me after this?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.42,0:04:59.62,Songs,,0,0,0,,Who could have predicted this reunion?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.62,0:05:07.50,Songs,,0,0,0,,I reel in this thread of memory, and use it to spin my tale
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.50,0:05:12.38,Songs,,0,0,0,,Why are you all pushy one minute,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.38,0:05:18.14,Songs,,0,0,0,,and then gentle the next?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.58,0:05:23.64,Songs,,0,0,0,,As long as the two of us share this secret
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.64,0:05:29.20,Songs,,0,0,0,,it will be the light that guides you
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.20,0:05:33.98,Songs,,0,0,0,,to somewhere in the yet-unknowable future
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.98,0:05:38.42,Songs,,0,0,0,,I'm telling you, it's okay to optimistic
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.42,0:05:42.46,Songs,,0,0,0,,I want to know everything about you
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.46,0:05:47.90,Songs,,0,0,0,,hidden deep within those eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.90,0:05:53.16,Songs,,0,0,0,,I can't control these feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.16,0:06:00.32,Songs,,0,0,0,,Piece by piece, my heart is being snatched away
